---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import ParallaxBanner from '../../components/ParallaxBanner.astro';
import ContactForm from '../../components/ContactForm.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Seguin Neighborhoods | Cody Posey Real Estate"
  description="Explore Seguin, TX neighborhoods by area and price range. From historic downtown to new construction communities — find the right fit for your lifestyle."
>
  <Navbar />
  <main style="padding-top: 80px;">

    <!-- Hero -->
    <div class="seg-hero">
      <div class="seg-hero__overlay"></div>
      <div class="seg-hero__content">
        <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
          <a href="/">Home</a> <span>/</span> <a href="/seguin/">Seguin</a> <span>/</span> <span>Neighborhoods</span>
        </nav>
        <h1>Seguin <span style="color:#FF1616;">Neighborhoods</span></h1>
        <p>Find the area that fits your lifestyle and budget</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Intro -->
    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="seg-page-intro seg-page-intro--centered">Seguin offers a range of neighborhoods — from established family communities and historic downtown living to newer construction and large-lot properties along the Guadalupe River. Here's how the city breaks down.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Neighborhoods -->
    <section class="section" style="background: var(--light-gray);">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title">
          <h2>Seguin <span class="accent">Neighborhoods</span></h2>
        </div>

        <div class="seg-area">
          <img src="/images/generated/neighborhoods/seg-nob-hill.png" alt="Nob Hill homes" class="seg-area__img" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="seg-area__header">
            <h3>Nob Hill</h3>
            <span class="seg-area__price">$250K - $350K</span>
          </div>
          <p>Primarily anchored by Nob Hill Condominiums, this established community offers a budget-friendly entry into homeownership in Seguin. The neighborhood features a tranquil atmosphere with mature trees and calmer streets, plus a community pool and clubhouse. Especially appealing to first-time buyers, Nob Hill is served by Seguin ISD.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="seg-area">
          <img src="/images/generated/neighborhoods/seg-mill-creek.png" alt="Village of Mill Creek homes" class="seg-area__img" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="seg-area__header">
            <h3>Village of Mill Creek</h3>
            <span class="seg-area__price">$200K - $320K</span>
          </div>
          <p>A quiet, family-friendly neighborhood with a close-knit vibe and larger lots than many surrounding communities. Village of Mill Creek offers easy access to New Braunfels, Randolph AFB, the Tesla factory, the Guadalupe River, and Lake McQueeney. Some sections have no HOA, and homes include a mix of one and two-story layouts. Served by Seguin ISD.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="seg-area">
          <img src="/images/generated/neighborhoods/seg-cordova-crossing.png" alt="Cordova Crossing homes" class="seg-area__img" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="seg-area__header">
            <h3>Cordova Crossing</h3>
            <span class="seg-area__price">$280K - $400K</span>
          </div>
          <p>A modern, family-friendly community with a relaxed neighborly atmosphere, wide streets, and sidewalks. Cordova Crossing features a playground, private dog park, and trails throughout the neighborhood. Homes showcase contemporary designs with open layouts, smart home technology, and energy-efficient construction. Served by Seguin ISD.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="seg-area">
          <img src="/images/generated/neighborhoods/seg-downtown.png" alt="Downtown Seguin homes" class="seg-area__img" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="seg-area__header">
            <h3>Downtown Seguin</h3>
            <span class="seg-area__price">$150K - $300K</span>
          </div>
          <p>Charming, walkable living in the heart of the city with access to boutiques, cafes, and restaurants along Main Street. Properties in the historic district include Victorian-era houses, bungalows, and mid-century ranches — each with its own character. Downtown Seguin is steeped in rich Texas history and is ideal for buyers who value character and convenience.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="seg-area">
          <img src="/images/generated/neighborhoods/seg-country-club.png" alt="Country Club Estates homes" class="seg-area__img" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="seg-area__header">
            <h3>Country Club Estates</h3>
            <span class="seg-area__price">$250K - $450K</span>
          </div>
          <p>Located near Seguin Country Club, this neighborhood offers an "open vista community" feel with pool and clubhouse amenities. An Architectural Review Committee maintains neighborhood standards, ensuring a well-kept and cohesive streetscape. Country Club Estates is a solid choice for buyers seeking an established neighborhood with recreational access. Served by Seguin ISD.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="seg-area">
          <img src="/images/generated/neighborhoods/seg-river-oaks.png" alt="River Oaks homes" class="seg-area__img" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="seg-area__header">
            <h3>River Oaks</h3>
            <span class="seg-area__price">$300K - $500K</span>
          </div>
          <p>A quiet, family-friendly neighborhood where some homes have waterfront access to Lake Seguin and the Guadalupe River, including boat docks. River Oaks features a diverse mix of properties — from vintage bungalows and postwar mid-century ranches to newer modern farmhouse and contemporary builds. A great option for buyers who want variety, water access, and a relaxed pace close to town.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- School District -->
    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title">
          <h2>School <span class="accent">District</span></h2>
          <p>Seguin's schools serve a growing and diverse community</p>
        </div>
        <div class="seg-schools__grid">
          <a href="https://www.seguin.k12.tx.us" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="seg-schools__card">
            <h3>Seguin ISD</h3>
            <p>Seguin ISD serves the city and surrounding areas with a focus on college readiness, career training, and community involvement. The district operates multiple campuses from pre-K through high school.</p>
            <span class="seg-schools__link">Visit Seguin ISD Website →</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="section" style="background: #000; color: #fff; text-align: center;">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Need Help <span class="accent">Narrowing It Down</span>?</h2>
        <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); max-width: 600px; margin: 1rem auto 2rem;">I can walk you through the differences between Seguin neighborhoods and help you focus your search on areas that match your priorities.</p>
        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-outline">Get Help Choosing a Neighborhood</a>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
  <ParallaxBanner image="/images/generated/porch-view.png" />

  <ContactForm context="I need help narrowing down Seguin neighborhoods..." />
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .seg-hero {
    position: relative;
    height: 280px;
    background: url('/images/generated/home-nb-ranch.png') center/cover no-repeat;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .seg-hero__overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.55);
  }

  .seg-hero__content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .seg-hero__content h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .seg-hero__content p {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .breadcrumb {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
  }

  .breadcrumb a {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .breadcrumb a:hover {
    color: #FF1616;
  }

  .breadcrumb span {
    margin: 0 0.3rem;
  }

  .seg-page-intro {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--gray);
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .seg-page-intro--centered {
    text-align: center;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--black);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* Neighborhood Cards */
  .seg-area {
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .seg-area__img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 200px;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .seg-area__header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding-left: 2rem;
    padding-right: 2rem;
  }

  .seg-area__header h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin: 0;
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .seg-area__price {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #FF1616;
    background: rgba(255,22,22,0.08);
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  .seg-area p {
    color: var(--gray);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    padding-left: 2rem;
    padding-right: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  /* Schools */
  .seg-schools__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .seg-schools__card {
    display: block;
    background: #fff;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .seg-schools__card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }

  .seg-schools__card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: #000;
  }

  .seg-schools__card:hover h3 {
    color: #FF1616;
  }

  .seg-schools__card p {
    color: var(--gray);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .seg-schools__link {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: #FF1616;
  }
</style>
